((Note Iron and tavatron I not going to get you killed I do have a plan even 
though it doesn't look like it there is one here.))

Tigerhawk Grins "You good but I'm better the walls in this cell are mirror 
coated graphite. Which means you can't fire your blasters in here and not 
have it reflect off the walls. Light in this room gets extremely bright. 
"Iron for once I asking you and Tavatron to trust me for once put the same 
trust you give plissanta and that you give Ramhorn and the others in me for a 
change." 

Tigerhawk Looks at DarkOne "Game Over " Tigerhawk pushes the buttons on both 
of the grenades and closes his eyes as he tosses them up they release a 
blinding flash of light bright to blind everyone in the room. In the moments 
of blindness Tigerhawk drops a cube and tosses something in Iron direction 
landing in one of her wound concealed as ((flash all figures would look like 
shadows)) A Shadowy Figure leaps out the hole Tigerhawk made and races down a 
hallway.  

When the light  fades A Tigerhawk stands picking his teeth with his finger 
Laughing harshly "Flash grenades I'm not about to kill myself. You you you 
you you don't Thhhhhhhhhhhiiiiiiiiiinnnnnnnnnnkkkkkkkkk this is the real me 
do you?" Sounding like a defective hologram like it must have been damaged in 
the entry. "By the tiiiiiiiiiiimmmmmmmmmmeeeeeee you watch this I be in the 
jungle."
